wiki.summary: “Pluto to Mars” was first previewed by Lil Uzi Vert on social media on November 25, 2020. With a fast-paced beat and a futuristic sound that matches space-themed lyrics, “Pluto to Mars” poses a fun and catchy track that showcases Uzi’s unique style and creativity. For some time rumored to release on Forever Young, the song was long-awaited by Uzi’s fanbase and saw some snippets being leaked around late 2022. It finally saw an official release on the Pink Tape. Read more on Last.fm.
